牌、聽聲 睇到後面就知<br />\n總之來講係一套少女熱血漫，因為條女就等如平時ge男主角<br />\n後期團隊戰果時係好熱血，都值得一睇 <br />\ncv都唔差 有mamo 有瀨戶 有細谷"},{"pid":"7d45473561ce18e85a43d10d103c89e20f9a2db0","tid":1296052,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84ea8e7f2acf6d7566d0526587c5b903da338947","tid":1296052,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"後面頂唔順 太一d少爺仔脾氣<br />\n棄棄地"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"係 好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前面明明好好睇 仲去過聖巡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c620bcbf5bbde11946f616a196ca27a4a37b014","tid":1296052,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d45473561ce18e85a43d10d103c89e20f9a2db0","tid":1296052,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84ea8e7f2acf6d7566d0526587c5b903da338947","tid":1296052,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"後面頂唔順 太一d少爺仔脾氣<br />\n棄棄地"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"係 好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前面明明好好睇 仲去過聖巡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"套野唔講感情線最好睇"},{"pid":"238e78b7714a553c871eea676f0567dd589f2ab0","tid":1296052,"uid":150649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"新派"},{"pid":"6c1f803bfdb61d5fbc67ff5c8109a3f4b660c400","tid":1296052,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c620bcbf5bbde11946f616a196ca27a4a37b014","tid":1296052,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d45473561ce18e85a43d10d103c89e20f9a2db0","tid":1296052,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84ea8e7f2acf6d7566d0526587c5b903da338947","tid":1296052,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:35:55.000